author: Virtual Reality Oasis
description:
The Ready Or Not VRO Mod is coming soon! This is a passion project I've been working on for some time. This mod is above and beyond what is possible with UEVR. The Ready Or Not VRO mod will be free and it will only work with the Steam version of the game. 

If you want to learn more about the Ready Or Not VRO Mod, join our Discord here; https://t.co/VbHAfb4Kme

I will be announcing the release date and more information on the mod on this channel soon! 

*READY OR NOT AND THE READY OR NOT LOGO ARE TRADEMARKS OR REGISTERED TRADEMARKS OF VOID INTERACTIVE* 

Thanks for watching []-)
